{"_path":"/maps/_ui/ai-assisted/ai-assisted","_dir":"ai-assisted","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"AI 辅助设计","description":"生成式 AI 在 UI 设计与原型制作中的应用","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子领域"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子领域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ui/ai-assisted/genai-for-ui-prototyping"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自助式UI原型设计与GenAI"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 利用生成式AI工具实现自助式UI原型设计的实践与思考"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 辅助设计正在改变 UI 设计的工作流程。从文本提示直接生成交互式原型，到智能设计建议与自动化布局，生成式 AI 工具正在降低设计门槛并加速创意迭代。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这些工具使产品经理和设计师能够快速将抽象概念转化为可测试的体验，缩短反馈循环并促进早期验证。然而，也需要警惕高保真原型可能带来的\"已完成\"错觉，以及代码质量与生产就绪性之间的鸿沟。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子领域","depth":2,"text":"子领域"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ui:ai-assisted:ai-assisted.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ui/ai-assisted/ai-assisted.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ui/ai-assisted/ai-assisted","_extension":"md"}